export default function calculateTime(t,l){try{let e=[t,l],a=0;for(let t of e){let[l,e,o]=t.split(":").map(parseFloat);a+=3600*l,a+=60*e,a+=o||0}let o=Math.floor(a/3600);a-=3600*o;let r=Math.floor(a/60);return a-=60*r,a<=9&&(a="0"+a),r<=9&&(r="0"+r),o<=9&&(o="0"+o),`${o}:${r}:${a}`}catch(t){console.warn("calculateTime Error: ",t)}}